    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>ABOUT THIS GAME</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Become an almighty <strong>Gladiator</strong> in this fast-paced Action Roguelike <strong>Crystalis Descendant</strong>. The <strong>Crystallisk</strong> are swarming the Arena and are out to destroy the vital <strong>Crystal</strong>. It is up to you to stop them!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Become stronger each time you face this relentless horde as you unlock newfound powers through their essence. Face the challenges of the <strong>Arena</strong> and uncover what lurks below.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187610/extras/10e9c1d80010bf8b8c896481a34d5610.poster.avif?t=1733216029\" width=616 height=313 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187610/extras/10e9c1d80010bf8b8c896481a34d5610.webm?t=1733216029\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>PROTECT THE CRYSTAL</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The <strong>Crystal</strong> is the heart of the <strong>Arena</strong> and the source of your power. Protect it at all costs and reap its rewards!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187610/extras/ad506d847538804a4190eda0932d3d5f.poster.avif?t=1733216029\" width=616 height=313 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187610/extras/ad506d847538804a4190eda0932d3d5f.webm?t=1733216029\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>CHARGE THE CRYSTAL AND UNLEASH ITS POWER</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gather <strong>Crystal Essence</strong> to charge the <strong>Crystal</strong> and unleash its devastating pulse to eliminate any remaining <strong>Crystallisk</strong> and proceed to unlock even greater powers!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187610/extras/d9fb235b91a19c32d3295f2a45518f55.poster.avif?t=1733216029\" width=616 height=313 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187610/extras/d9fb235b91a19c32d3295f2a45518f55.webm?t=1733216029\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FACE HORDES OF CRYSTALLISK</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From raging <strong>Ravagers</strong> to indomitable <strong>Ironscales</strong>. Face a great variety of crystal monsters known as the <strong>Crystallisk</strong>, each with their own attacks and skills. Be prepared to face trials and challenges as they are out to defeat you to get to the <strong>Crystal</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187610/extras/41dcfcc37a52f4d319dd31b305770532.poster.avif?t=1733216029\" width=616 height=313 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187610/extras/41dcfcc37a52f4d319dd31b305770532.webm?t=1733216029\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>USE YOUR SURROUNDINGS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the <strong>Arena</strong> to your advantage and destroy the environment using it to outsmart the horde by blocking their path.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187610/extras/8baa20af74fae81f43cf81852963c768.poster.avif?t=1733216029\" width=616 height=313 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187610/extras/8baa20af74fae81f43cf81852963c768.webm?t=1733216029\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>UNLEASH POWERFUL UPGRADES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Become a <strong>Poison</strong> master, gain a thirst for blood or perhaps, become a <strong>Void</strong> fanatic as you unlock new upgrades and fight your way through each wave! Discover you own playstyle with over 80 upgrades and many more to come!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>CONQUER THE MUTATIONS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You never know what lurks in the depths while descending into the <strong>Arena</strong>. These <strong>Mutations</strong> are giant aberrations which have been roaming underground for aeons and are awaiting to devour new <strong>Gladiators</strong> coming their way.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187610/extras/1c18c9af63dd623696036181e9ce82cb.poster.avif?t=1733216029\" width=616 height=313 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187610/extras/1c18c9af63dd623696036181e9ce82cb.webm?t=1733216029\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>BECOME AN ALMIGHTY GLADIATOR</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Be the <strong>Gladiator</strong> that resides within you. Experiment with different builds, unlock new weapons and characters with each their own unique playstyle. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FORGE GAME-CHANGING ENHANCEMENTS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Return to the <strong>Sanctuary</strong> and use the <strong>Forge</strong> to craft new enhancements for your abilities, weapons, and even the <strong>Crystal</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>ROADMAP</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover our plans for the future! Take a look at our roadmap to see what exciting updates and content we have in store for <strong>Crystalis Descendant</strong>. We're committed to delivering a thrilling and evolving experience for our players.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187610/extras/5b0b12ae6ece90d80020dbf4972e4874.avif?t=1733216029\" width=616 height=1360 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some thanks are definitely in order!  We are a small team developing games we love, so we would like to thank you and our amazing community for all the support so far. Without you, we wouldn't be here.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
